.TH ABRAFLEXI-TRANSACTION-REPORT 1 "July 17, 2026" "abraflexi-matcher" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
abraflexi-transaction-report \- Generate a bank transaction report from AbraFlexi in JSON format
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-transaction-report
.RB [ \-o
.IR output_file ]
.RB [ \-\-output= "" output_file "" ]
.RB [ \-e
.IR env_file ]
.RB [ \-\-environment= "" env_file "" ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B abraflexi-transaction-report
lists bank transactions recorded in AbraFlexi for the configured scope
(by default, yesterday) and writes them as a JSON report. It performs no
matching; use it for reconciliation exports or feeding transactions into
another system.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output = \fIFILE\fR
Write the JSON report to
.I FILE
instead of the location given by
.B RESULT_FILE
(or stdout).
.TP
.BR \-e ", " \-\-environment = \fIFILE\fR
Load configuration from
.I FILE
instead of
.B ../.env
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_URL
AbraFlexi server URL
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_LOGIN
AbraFlexi login username
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_PASSWORD
AbraFlexi password
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_COMPANY
AbraFlexi company code
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_BANK
AbraFlexi bank account code to report on.
.TP
.B REPORT_SCOPE
Period to report on, e.g.
.B yesterday
(default),
.B today ,
or another value understood by AbraFlexi's bank statement scope selector.
.TP
.B RESULT_FILE
Path to the output JSON report file (default: transaction-report.json)
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success \- transaction report generated successfully.
.TP
.B 1
General error \- unexpected error occurred (retryable).
.TP
.B 2
Connection error \- unable to connect to the AbraFlexi server (critical, retryable).
.TP
.B 3
I/O error \- failed to write the output file.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I transaction-report.json
Default output file containing the list of bank transactions in JSON format compliant with the multiflexi report schema.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR abraflexi-pull-bank (1),
.BR abraflexi-matcher (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Written by Vitex Software.
